[18/10/2018 14:06:27] <font color="#00ff00">Vamos, vamos...</font>
[18/10/2018 14:06:27] <font color="#00ffff">No...</font>
[18/10/2018 14:06:30] <font color="#00ff00">¡Quieta, Sabel!</font>
[18/10/2018 14:06:30] <font color="#00ffff">Ah.</font>
